{"tid":225512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[健身]有冇人手肘有事從來都練唔到三頭","createTime":"2017-05-01T21:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T16:41:57.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c89ecf5e61981d958338334b373c7bae07c6b3e7","tid":225512,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:02:15.000Z","msg":"手肘有事 用4-6lbs dumbell都痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e98166b95028607677e5039d434fec306c56d3","tid":225512,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手肘有事 用4-6lbs dumbell都痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用機練三頭會痛"},{"pid":"1c9ac561c93b08d31e8cf7e475e5cb5f637018fc","tid":225512,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手肘有事 用4-6lbs dumbell都痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用機練三頭會痛</blockquote><br />\n我就係9年前第一次做gym<br />\n<br />\n果時係極瘦撚 3頭應該咩力都無 玩機玩得太重手肘奶左野到而家<br />\n<br />\n左手做4lbs會痛 右手好d 去到12lbs<br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位瘦撚小心d 明知自己瘦咪玩咁重一開始"},{"pid":"ee4011b465daa315a0be67110c6e05983228ffba","tid":225512,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手肘有事 用4-6lbs dumbell都痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用機練三頭會痛</blockquote><br />\n幾多lbs開始痛 左右手肘都係?"},{"pid":"e0bd812f476489fc81ec274184d0dafa0a4b7a09","tid":225512,"uid":6307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手肘有事 用4-6lbs dumbell都痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抖一排都好唔番？"},{"pid":"a7de73b1492220806f9c55d1aba42c9460486cfc","tid":225512,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:18